    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Cut your\u00a0<strong>leek[s]</strong> in half and wash carefully to remove any grit from between the leaves, then top, tail and slice very finely</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong>\u00a0over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once\u00a0melted, add the<strong>\u00a0sliced leek</strong>, a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>\u00a0and 30ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[45ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\">\u00a0[60ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong>, then cook for 5 min or until the water has evaporated</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> (skins on) in half</p><p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 15-20 min or until fork-tender</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot to steam dry</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel the skin off your<strong>\u00a0smoked\u00a0mackerel fillet[s]</strong>\u00a0and discard</p><p>Flake the <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>mackerel</strong> into very small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Combine\u00a0the<strong> flaked mackerel </strong>in a bowl with your <strong>soft cheese</strong>,\u00a0<strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and <strong>cooked leek</strong>, reserve the pan</p><p>Season with a pinch of both\u00a0<strong>salt</strong>\u00a0and\u00a0<strong>pepper</strong>, knead well and divide the mixture equally,<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>then shape into patties \u2013 these are your<strong>\u00a0smoked mackerel fishcake[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a low heat with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]\u00a0</span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the\u00a0<strong>smoked mackerel</strong> <strong>fishcake[s]</strong>\u00a0and cook for 3-4 min on each side until browned and crispy, adding more\u00a0<strong>vegetable\u00a0oil</strong>\u00a0if needed</p><p>Tip: Flip gently and resist moving the patties so they hold their shape!</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>dill</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely (keep both herbs separate)</p><p>Cut your\u00a0<strong>apple[s]</strong>\u00a0(skin on) into very fine matchsticks</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>,<strong> chopped dill </strong>and\u00a0the <strong>apple matchsticks</strong> with a pinch of<strong> pepper </strong>\u2013\u00a0this is your<strong>\u00a0apple remoulade</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, the <strong>chopped chives</strong> and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong> to the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> and give everything a good mix up \u2013 these are your <strong>herby potatoes</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/smoked-mackerel-fishcake-potatoes-and-apple-remoulade/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoked</strong> <strong>mackerel\u00a0fishcake</strong> with the <strong>herby potatoes</strong> and <strong>apple remoulade</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
